desc: Based on its location in a small predominantly rural gmina of the Ciechanów district (Mazowieckie) with limited higher‐education–driven industries and commuter links we’d place Ościsłowo 30A in the “Low” class for share of university graduates.

Thus it falls into the “High” bracket.

I would classify Goleniów (Goleniowski) at the “Medium” level.
